tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE employee_engagement_data ( 
  employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  engagement_score FLOAT, 
  engagement_date DATE 
)

CREATE TABLE hr_initiatives ( 
  initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  initiative_name VARCHAR(50), 
  initiative_description TEXT 
)

CREATE TABLE employee_feedback ( 
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  employee_id INT, 
  feedback_text TEXT, 
  feedback_date DATE 
)

CREATE TABLE employee_demographics (
    employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    department VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE hr_initiatives (
    initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(100),
    initiative_category VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Employee { 
 id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
 name VARCHAR(50), 
 department VARCHAR(50), 
 hire_date DATE, 
 engagement_score INT 
 }
